{"tid":2018673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［國際戰線］入嚟睇吓外媒點報監察會份偽中立報告","createTime":"2020-05-15T18:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T02:57:31.000Z","uid":82387,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ab14acdea98a63aee4306e7f4b3987edc815ed67","tid":2018673,"uid":82387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T18:13:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>Reuters 路透社</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong leader rejects protesters' call for independent police probe<br />\n</strong> <br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-police/hong-kong-leader-rejects-protesters-call-for-independent-police-probe-idUSKBN22R0S8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-police%2Fhong-kong-leader-rejects-protesters-call-for-independent-police-probe-idUSKBN22R0S8&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=f4e2cd96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-police%2Fhong-kong-leader-rejects-protesters-call-for-independent-police-probe-idUSKBN22R0S8&h=744be71c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-police/hong-kong-leader-rejects-protesters-call-for-independent-police-probe-idUSKBN22R0S8</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n除咗講返黑警用不對等武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&quot;The report has turned a blind eye to<span style=\"color: red;\"> disproportional police brutality,</span>&quot; pro-democracy lawmaker Fernando Cheung said.<br />\n<br />\n仲鞭屍上星期和你shop要記者跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPolice handling of protests came under fresh scrutiny at the weekend when officers <span style=\"color: red;\">pepper-sprayed journalists and made some kneel</span> in a cordoned-off area. In a rare move, the police chief said on Tuesday his officers should have acted more professionally.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Bloomberg彭博+TIME 時代雜誌</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong Watchdog Defends Police Actions, Chides Protesters</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-05-15/hong-kong-police-watchdog-to-release-report-on-protest-conduct\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-05-15%2Fhong-kong-police-watchdog-to-release-report-on-protest-conduct&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=d0345a9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-05-15/hong-kong-police-watchdog-to-release-report-on-protest-conduct</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong&rsquo;s Police Watchdog Largely Exonerates Officers and Blames Protesters</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://time.com/5837300/hong-kong-police-ipcc-report/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F5837300%2Fhong-kong-police-ipcc-report%2F&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=bff475d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/5837300/hong-kong-police-ipcc-report/</a><br />\n<br />\n一嚟就話份報告幫黑警護航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\na lengthy four-volume report Friday that<span style=\"color: red;\"> mainly defended the police force&rsquo;s response to the often violent unrest that rocked the Asian financia</span>l hub last year<br />\n<br />\n仲有提返舊年國際特赦組織份香港報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAmnesty International report alleging officers<span style=\"color: red;\"> beat up and even &ldquo;tortured&rdquo; detained protesters,</span> while also rejecting criticism of the way they&rsquo;ve handled probes into rape and sexual assault allegations by demonstrators.<br />\n<br />\nThe police have rejected accusations that its officers acted unprofessionally, and very few of them were suspended or disciplined. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Nikkei Asian Review 日本經濟新聞</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong police watchdog backs controversial handling of protests<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://asia.nikkei.com/Spotlight/Hong-Kong-protests/Hong-Kong-police-watchdog-backs-controversial-handling-of-protests\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FSpotlight%2FHong-Kong-protests%2FHong-Kong-police-watchdog-backs-controversial-handling-of-protests&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=09977a01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asia.nikkei.com/Spotlight/Hong-Kong-protests/Hong-Kong-police-watchdog-backs-controversial-handling-of-protests</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n講返份報告並冇滿足大眾訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThe report fell short of expectations from the public and government critics, who have been calling for <span style=\"color: red;\">a legally binding and independent inquiry into alleged police brutality</span><br />\n<br />\n有quote埋民記嘅comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA group of demonstrators have called the IPCC a &quot;toothless commission&quot; and a &quot;joke&quot; as it is <span style=\"color: red;\">not empowered with rights to gather evidence or call witnesses.</span><br />\n<br />\n結論：大家都心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cd9f7fd705d9f6ecc3fef0f425aa2ff98bbee0","tid":2018673,"uid":163937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T18:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa17b289123d0a992a4feb7b545727b81ba0499","tid":2018673,"uid":82387,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T18:21:59.000Z","msg":"Twitter手足follow埋記者Twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JessiePang0125\" data